Welcome to FTPoverHTTP’s documentation!¶

Introduction¶

For our third semester of DUT Informatique, we had for project to make an API to use FTP commands through HTTP request. We make 3 differents versions but only 2 are documented and usable. Also, if you have any request or bug report, please contact us at mael.caubere@etu.univ-nantes.fr
